name: Keep Them Dead
description:
A fast paced fps which was made in a span of 3 days. In the game your goal is to go to the end of the level but there are some robots attacking you have 4 guns to defend yourself but the guns won't kill the enemies instead they can only stun them for sometime now its up to you to reach the end. Good Luck!

Source : https://github.com/Ishan034/Keep-Them-Dead
